hmm..today in general was pretty uneventful.  i spent alot of time on the computer, playing guitar, and playing super mario kart.  im getting pretty good at mario kart.  im on 150cc, which is like impossible.

im supposed to be reading "the catcher in the rye" in american studies.  but i have decided that i am not going to read it.  i know you are probably all saying "you dumbass, that book is so good, read it."  im sure it is a good book, and im sure ill read it someday, but theres just something about being told how many pages to read, then writing a summary on what i read, then making group questions based on the reading that pisses me off.  so therefore, i wont be reading.  i bought cliffnotes, i'll be reading those.

i think im a little too excited for saturday.
